Documentation.name: VL_Connectors_UMLProfile
Documentation.notes: Connectors used accross Videotron architecture diagrams

Tag.name: Impact
Tag.description: "Impact" which defines the degree of impact on scale of 1 to 5 (5 = highest impact)

Tag.name: ImpactType
Tag.description: "Type of impact" which defines AMUD (Add, Modify, Use, Delete)

Tag.name: AllocatedInvestmentDollarsCaptured
Tag.description: "Allocated Investment $ Captured". Mutually exclusive with AllocatedInvestmentDollarsDerived

Tag.name: AllocatedInvestmentPercent
Tag.description: "Allocated Investment %" which defines the % of the total investment of the work package that is allocated to each related capability

Tag.name: AllocatedInvestmentDollarsDerived
Tag.description: "Allocated Investment $ Derived" which is derived from the "Allocated Investment %" and the Investment attribute of the initiative. Mutually exclusive with AllocatedInvestmentDollarsCaptured.

Documentation.notes: UML profile aimed to build Motivation level objects in Videotron

Documentation.name: VL_Strategy_UMLProfile
Documentation.notes: UML profile aimed to build Strategy level objects in Videotron

Tag.name: Acronym
Tag.description: A surname of code that uniquely identify the system.

Tag.name: AssignedArchitect
Tag.description: Name of the System Architect in charge of the system.

Tag.name: Classification
Tag.description: Main classification of the role of the system. Values: CF,NF,BF,TOOL,MiddleWare

Tag.name: GlobalEvolution
Tag.description: Global Rating on the capacity of the system to evolve

Tag.name: Grouping
Tag.description: Keyword to group a set of systems to a topic or top level system identifier. For example: SAP for each modules or subsystems integrated with.

Tag.name: HostingType
Tag.description: Identify how the System is hosted: Values: INT, EXT, SaaS, PaaS, IaaS, DaaS

Tag.name: MainBusinessUnit
Tag.description: Name of the main business unit or top level organization entity that uses or depends on the system.
Tag.values: Affaires,ING Dev App,ING Marcel Kabongo,ING Mourad,ING SGR,ING Systèmes IP&_c_^ Serveurs et Stockage,ING Tel IP,ING Video,SuperClub

Tag.name: Owner_TechnicalSector
Tag.description: Top Technical entity that owns the system or technology. It usually identifies the Vice-presidency.

Tag.name: Responsible_Operations
Tag.description: Name of the group or individual responsible for operating the system.

Tag.name: Supplier
Tag.description: Name or identification of the system's supplier. (IBM, Oracle, ...)

Tag.name: TechnicalOwner_Software
Tag.description: Name of the group or individual that is responsaible for the system's software.

Tag.name: TechnicalOwner_Software_Comments
Tag.description: Comments registered by the Technical Software Owner. This is usually notes or supplemental information about the system.

Tag.name: TechnicalQuality_Infra
Tag.description: Rating of the technical infrastructure quality.

Tag.name: VL_CMDB_Ref
Tag.description: GUID of CMDB reference when available.
